76561198018589819,Recommended,269030,9374222,"Posted: 7 March, 2014",all,Darkfinity,"This is such a fantastic game! Don't you dare be put off by the low price or the people saying it's too short. This is a game that one can simply stop playing.It has a fun, comedy board game style that will make you nostalgic and feel happy. The music is beautiful, and to top all that off there's the one unique point of this game that is done so well:It's not about getting to the end, it's about enjoying what you have whilst you still have it. That, my friends, is a fantastic message about life. You're playing a fable! You simply don't lose the game.Now, people will play it for different reasons. At first, you play it to make sure there's a good ending. Overtime, you get this idea that actually it's not about that. You make moral choices, you choose your fate. What your character becomes is a reflection of how you play it, and trust me, there's some really great twists and turns to the game.My favourite part is that what one player does directly influences what happens to the other, thus making it a team game. Play with your friends, play with yourself, it's fun both ways for different reasons. Top game of the season, game of the year so far for me.So, what are you waiting for? Buy it!"
